        "created_at": "2022-08-07T18:40:29.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>One I haven\u2019t heard before although I don\u2019t pay as much attention as I used to so maybe this is old news.  My personal experience is that I had a bunch of \u201803/\u201804 D\u2019Auvenay under wax that didn\u2019t make it to middle age, but I can see an argument that those vintages weren\u2019t for the long haul anyway so are perhaps not the right test.<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.frw.co.uk/editorial/people/solving-premox-problem-olivier-lamy?utm_campaign=Brand%20%E2%80%93%20other%20communications&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;_hsmi=222013076&amp;_hsenc=p2ANqtz-9FyvaY0bePY7FakXdtERhJPPL84qwciQTem9Neskk1P7ssH7BPhwLFoPMstx7qKVZqN5OOlI24KQtWos8SS9LNwcWhXe_LHIAIXyYwC4ZZ6LF88PI&amp;utm_content=221946742&amp;utm_source=hs_email\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://www.frw.co.uk/editorial/people/solving-premox-problem-olivier-lamy?utm_campaign=Brand%20\u2013%20other%20communications&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;_hsmi=222013076&amp;_hsenc=p2ANqtz-9FyvaY0bePY7FakXdtERhJPPL84qwciQTem9Neskk1P7ssH7BPhwLFoPMstx7qKVZqN5OOlI24KQtWos8SS9LNwcWhXe_LHIAIXyYwC4ZZ6LF88PI&amp;utm_content=221946742&amp;utm_source=hs_email</a></p>",
