        "id": 3862758,
        "name": "Jayson Cohen",
        "username": "Jayson_Cohen",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/j/8797f3/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2022-08-07T20:23:37.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=133614\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/original/3X/e/8/e87148ebcd1df56551c495d1105f732d10f7da42.png\" class=\"site-icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=133614\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"10:38PM - 26 October 2016\">WineBerserkers \u2013 26 Oct 16</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db3686/original/1X/973cca6246737ae55b5ad7fbc6bddc245f0ca306.png\" class=\"thumbnail onebox-avatar\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\">\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=133614\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Do wax capsules effect aging?</a></h3>\n\n  <p>I have no perspective or experience with this, but it seems to me the additional air barrier would cause wax sealed bottles to age more slowly than others.  Any thoughts?</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
